'''費米輝光'''是顆粒發出的強烈[[紫外線|紫外線]]<ref name=ref1>"[http://www.spacetelescope.org/news/heic9911/ The Heliosphere is Tilted - implications for the 'Galactic Weather Forecast'?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.spacetelescope.org/news/heic9911/ |date=20200921162319 }}". [http://www.spacetelescope.org/about/ Hubble] {{Wayback|url=http://www.spacetelescope.org/about/ |date=20201221015335 }}. 13 March 2000.</ref>，通常是來自[[太陽系|太陽系]][[弓形震波|弓形震波]]的[[氫|氫]]<ref name=ref3/>。是來自恆星和太陽的光進入[[日球層頂|日球層頂]]（heliopause）和[[星際物質|星際物質]]之間的區域時<ref name=ref2>"[http://www.space.com/scienceastronomy/solarsystem/heliosphere_shock_000315.html A Glowing Discovery at the Forefront of Our Plunge Through Space] {{Wayback|url=http://www.space.com/scienceastronomy/solarsystem/heliosphere_shock_000315.html |date=20010111053400 }}". [[SPACE.com|SPACE.com]]. 15 March 2000.</ref>，經歷[[費米加速|費米加速]]<ref name=ref3>"[http://bric.postech.ac.kr/myboard/read.php?Board=news&id=31674&Page=733&PARA0=5&SOURCE=&PARA15=&FindIt=&FindText= Where the Solar Wind Hits the Wall] {{Wayback|url=http://bric.postech.ac.kr/myboard/read.php?Board=news&id=31674&Page=733&PARA0=5&SOURCE=&PARA15=&FindIt=&FindText= |date=20110721110439 }}". [http://bric.postech.ac.kr/about/greeting/index.php BRIC] {{Wayback|url=http://bric.postech.ac.kr/about/greeting/index.php |date=20090409015000 }}. 20 March 2000.</ref>，在過渡區蹦來蹦去好幾回，通過與星際物質中的原子碰撞獲得能量所產生的。費米輝光和弓形震波的第一個證據，得力於[[航海家1號|航海家1號]]<ref name=ref1/><ref name=ref2/>和[[哈伯太空望遠鏡|哈伯太空望遠鏡]]<ref name=ref1/><ref name=ref2/>的觀測。

在2012年，來自[[星際邊界探測器|星際邊界探測器]]衛星和[[航海家1號|航海家1號]]與[[航海家2號|航海家2號]]所蒐集的資料，顯示太陽目前在星際物質環境中運動的速度還不夠快，尚不足以形成弓形震波<ref name=physorg20120511>{{citation | title=New Interstellar Boundary Explorer data show heliosphere's long-theorized bow shock does not exist | date=May 10, 2012 | work=Phys.org | url=http://phys.org/news/2012-05-interstellar-boundary-explorer-heliosphere-long-theorized.html | accessdate=2012-02-11 | archive-date=2012-07-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120719164440/http://phys.org/news/2012-05-interstellar-boundary-explorer-heliosphere-long-theorized.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

